	<Title>
		Want healthier recipes? Swap ingredients!
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;A simple switch of ingredients can turn fatty family favorites into healthy dishes. Substitute turkey bacon or lean prosciutto for bacon. Replace sour cream with fat-free plain yogurt. Try lean ground turkey or chicken instead of ground beef. And use applesauce or prune puree for half of the called-for butter, shortening or oil in baked goods.&lt;/p&gt;
